    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "buriburi",
      "speakerName": "ブリ山ブリスケ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-buriburi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-buriburi013.m4a",
      "text": "くっ……せっかく遊びに来てくれたのに\n争いに巻き込んでしまって申し訳ない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2666666348,
      "endTime": 20.4799981434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "私達は大丈夫。ブリスケが守ってくれたから。それより\nブリスケの体が心配……傷だらけでボロボロ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6666649818,
      "endTime": 31.646665287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "buriburi",
      "speakerName": "ブリ山ブリスケ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-buriburi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-buriburi014.m4a",
      "text": "ブリブリッ……雫ちゃんは優しいブリね\nオラは強いから大丈夫！　それじゃあ……お元気で！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.83333203,
      "endTime": 43.5799977938,
      "sfxList": [
